==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Non prosequitur
<hw>Non" pro*seq"ui*tur</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[L. he does not
prosecute.]</ety> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>A judgment entered against the
plaintiff in a suit where he does not appear to prosecute. See <er>Nolle
prosequi</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>nonreciprocating</ent>⟦br⟧
